datasets.name: dataset1
queryLines: SELECT * FROM land_market_dev.`30_datamart`.transaction_detail where land_uid not like 'P2020%' order by land_uid desc;

datasets.name: 4a0d3c7d
queryLines:
select date_format(td.lease_date, 'yyyy') as lease_year,
       date_format(td.lease_date, 'MM') as lease_month,
       'Q' || date_format(td.lease_date, 'q') as lease_quarter,
       td.land_area_sqm,
       nvl(td.building_area_sqm, td.land_area_sqm * 2) as building_area_sqm,
       dlu.land_use_categories,
       td.lease_price_paid / 10000 as lease_price_paid_10k,
       nvl(td.building_area_sqm, td.land_area_sqm * 2) / td.land_area_sqm as building_plot_ratio,
       td.lease_price_paid / td.land_area_sqm as price_per_sqm,
       case when dlu.land_use_categories like '%住宅类%' then 'customer' 
            when dlu.land_use_categories like '%商业类%' then 'business' 
            else 'industrial' end as land_type,
       land_owner
 from land_market_dev.30_datamart.transaction_detail as td
 left join land_market_dev.`30_datamart`.dim_land_use as dlu on td.land_uid = dlu.land_uid
 where date_format(td.lease_date, 'yyyy') > 2020

datasets.name: e138ae07
queryLines:
with min_price_per_sql as (
SELECT *, lease_price_paid / land_area_sqm as price_per_sqm, (lease_price_paid -  lease_price) / lease_price as premium_rate, 'min_price_per_sqm' as price_per_sql_category, building_area_sqm / land_area_sqm as plot_ratio, substring(land_location, 1, instr(land_location, '区')) as district
FROM land_market_dev.`30_datamart`.transaction_detail 
where land_uid not like 'P2020%' order by lease_price_paid / land_area_sqm 
limit 10),

max_price_per_sql as (
SELECT *, lease_price_paid / land_area_sqm as price_per_sqm, (lease_price_paid -  lease_price) / lease_price as premium_rate, 'max_price_per_sqm' as price_per_sql_category, building_area_sqm / land_area_sqm as plot_ratio, substring(land_location, 1, instr(land_location, '区')) as district
FROM land_market_dev.`30_datamart`.transaction_detail 
where land_uid not like 'P2020%' order by lease_price_paid / land_area_sqm desc
limit 10)

SELECT * FROM min_price_per_sql
union
SELECT * FROM max_price_per_sql
